### Authentication Endpoints

# Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "John Customer",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "address": "123 Main St, City, State",
  "role": "CUSTOMER"
}

